Turai ta ci gaba da ci 10-6 kafin ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder Cup
Turai na kan gaba sosai a ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder Cup bayan da suka yi nasara da Amurka a wasannin kwallon kafa da na hudu a ranar Asabar, 10-6.
Manyan 'yan wasa biyu Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari sun jagoranci gasar ta lashe gasar ta biyu a kan Tiger Woods, kuma sun kara maki hudu a gasar Le Golf National a yau.
Thomas Bjorn, dan wasan Turai, wanda ya yi kokari sosai don ya ci nasara bayan ya yi rashin nasara a Hazeltin shekaru biyu da suka gabata, ya yi nasara a kan tawagar Amurka da ke cikin damuwa a wasan kwallon kwando na safe, inda suka kai wasan 3-1.
Amurka ta fi kowacce a gasar ta hudu, inda ta ci biyu, amma ba ta iya rage matsayinta ba.
Jim Fury ya bukaci maki takwas daga wasanni 12 na biyu a ranar Lahadi don ya ci nasara.
Fleetwood shine farkon dan wasan Turai da ya ci maki hudu a jere. Shi da Molinari, wanda kuma aka sani da suna Molliwood, sun kasance biyu na biyu a tarihin Ryder Cup bayan karshen mako mai ban mamaki, wanda ya ci maki hudu a wasanni huɗu na farko.
Bayan sun farfasa Woods da Patrick Reed a wasan kwallon kwando, sai suka gama da Woods da Bryson Dechambeau, dan wasan Amurka, da suka yi sanyin gwiwa, da ƙwazo sosai, 5-4.
Woods, wanda ya sha wahala a wasan biyu da ya yi a ranar Asabar, ya yi fice a wasu lokatai, amma ya yi rashin nasara a wasanni 19 daga cikin wasanni 29 da ya yi a wasan kwallon kwando da na hudu, har ma a wasanni bakwai a jere.
Justin Rose ya huta da safe, amma ya koma wasan hudu tare da Henrik Stenson, amma ya rasa 2-1 ga Dustin Johnson da Brooks Koepka, waɗanda ke matsayi na farko da na uku.
