Game of Thrones star Kit Harington ya kai hari ga wani nau'i na maza da ke da guba
Kit Harington sananne ne saboda rawar da ya taka a matsayin Jon Snow a wasan kwaikwayo na HBO mai ban tsoro Game of Thrones.
Harrington ya yi ta kai hari ga irin wannan hali na mutum mai son mata: dan wasan mai shekaru 31 ya ce irin wadannan ayyuka suna ba yara maza damar jin cewa dole ne su yi aiki tuƙuru don samun girmamawa.
