Harrington, wanda kwanan nan ma yana cikin 'yan jarida na Game of Thrones, kuma wanda ya auri Rose Leslie, 'yar shekara 31, ya yarda cewa yana da muradin shiga cikin batun.
"Tambayar inda muka yi kuskure game da mazauni tana da matukar tasiri a gare ni a yanzu", in ji shi.
Me aka koya wa maza a shekarun da suka girma da ya kai ga matsalolin da ake gani a yanzu?
