HIV/AIDS: An samu ƙaruwar kamuwa da cutar a China da kashi 14
Kasar Sin ta ba da rahoton cewa yawan mutanen da ke da cutar HIV da kuma cutar AIDS ya ƙaru da kashi 14 bisa ɗari.
Hukumar kiwon lafiya ta ce cutar ta shafi rayukan mutane fiye da 820,000 a ƙasar.
An samu sabbin mutane kusan 40,000 a kwata na biyu na 2018 kadai.
Mafi yawan sababbin cututtuka sun kasance ta hanyar jima'i, wanda ke nuna canji a cikin bayanan da suka gabata.
A al'adance, cutar HIV ta yaɗu da sauri a wasu sassan ƙasar Sin ta hanyar jinin da ke da ƙwayoyin cuta.
Amma, a wani taron da aka yi a lardin Yunnan, jami'an kiwon lafiya na kasar Sin sun ce, an rage kamuwa da cutar HIV kusan zuwa sifili ta wannan hanyar.
Amma, shekara guda bayan haka, adadin mutanen da ke kamuwa da cutar HIV da kuma AIDS a China ya ƙaru da 100,000.
Cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i ta zama gagarumar matsala a cikin al'ummar LGBT na kasar Sin.
An yi wa luwadi yancin yin jima'i a kasar Sin a shekarar 1997, amma an ce ana nuna wa mutanen LGBT wariya.
Bincike ya nuna cewa saboda ra'ayoyin da suka dace da al'adun ƙasar, kashi 70  90% na maza da suke yin jima'i da maza suna yin aure da mata.
Yawancin cututtuka suna faruwa ne domin rashin kāriya a irin waɗannan dangantaka.
Tun 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin samar da magungunan cutar kanjamau ga kowa, a matsayin wani ɓangare na matakan magance matsalar.
Maxine Waters ta musanta cewa wani dan majalisar dattijai ne ya fitar da bayanan da suka shafi 'yan jam'iyyar Republican, inda ta zarge shi da yada "karya mai hadari" da kuma "ka'idojin hada-hada".
A ranar Asabar, 'yar majalisar wakilai ta Amurka, Maxine Waters ta musanta zargin cewa ma'aikacinta ta wallafa bayanan sirri na wasu 'yan majalisar wakilai uku a shafukan Wikipedia da suka shafi su.
Dan majalisa na Democrat daga Los Angeles ya tabbatar da cewa masu sharhi da shafukan yanar gizo na 'yancin-kai-kai' ne ke yada maganganun.
Waters ya ce a cikin wata sanarwa da ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter.
An ce wasu cikin bayanan da aka fitar sun ƙunshi adireshin gida da kuma lambobin waya na Lindsey Graham, 'yar Majalisar Dattawa a South Carolina, da Mike Lee da Orrin Hatch, 'yan Majalisar Dattawa a Utah.
Wani mutum da ba a san sunansa ba ne ya fitar da bayanan a ranar Alhamis a gaban kwamitin majalisar dattawa na Amurka, a lokacin da ake sauraron karar da aka yi wa dan takarar kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh, kan zargin da ake yi masa na cin zarafin mata.
Wannan fitowar ta faru ne bayan wasu 'yan majalisar dattawa uku sun yi wa Kavanaugh tambayoyi.
Shafukan yanar gizo masu ra'ayin mazan jiya kamar su Gateway Pundit da RedState sun ruwaito cewa, a cewar jaridar Hill, an wallafa sakonnin ne daga adireshin IP da ke da alaƙa da ofishin Waters kuma wani daga cikin ma'aikatan Waters ne ya wallafa.
