Wannan zargi da ba shi da tushe ba, ba gaskiya ba ne kuma karya ce.
Sanarwar Waters ta yi sanadin taurin kai a intanet, kuma masu sukar sun hada da tsohon sakataren yada labarai na fadar White House Ari Fleischer.
"Hanyar da yake ƙin yarda da hakan ta yi muni sosai", in ji Fleischer.
