Johnny English ya sake kai hari a wani abin dariya na Rowan Atkinson
An riga an kafa al'ada ta neman maganganun Brexit a kowane fim da ke da ɗan ƙaramin ɗanɗano a cikin Burtaniya, amma wannan bai dace da satar ɗan leken asirin Johnny English da kuma jerin wasan kwaikwayo na wasan kwaikwayo ba, wanda ya fara a 2003 tare da Johnny English kuma ya sake farfadowa a cikin 2011 na gaba Johnny English  Reincarnated.
Shin harshe na satir na al'umma da aka yi wa dariya zai iya zama sabon nasarar fitar da ƙasashen waje na Burtaniya?
Ko ta yaya, mai kallon ido, mai son magana, kuma marar iyawa Johnny English ya riga ya sami izinin sake yin fim ɗin, wanda sunansa ya nuna cewa wannan fim ɗin yana da ban dariya da ke nufin kasuwar fim ɗin da ba Turanci ba.
Hakika, wannan ɗan leƙen asiri ne mai son yaɗa abin da ke cikin zuciyarsa, amma ya zama kamar mai duba Clouseau ne, Mr. Beani, da kuma ɗan mawaƙa mai ƙyalli a bikin buɗewa na London a shekara ta 2012.
A cikin wannan hali, akwai wani mutum mai ban mamaki da kuma masanin duniya wanda ya bar rikici a baya, wanda Atkinson ya fara nunawa a cikin tallan TV na Barclaycard da aka manta.
Amma, a wasan karshe, akwai lokacin da za a yi.
Na fi son wurin da Johnny English ya zo da jirgin sama mai saukar ungulu a cikin makamai na zamanin da, kuma a lokacin da aka yi masa katako a kan kwalkwali.
Kyautar Atkinson ta wasan kwaikwayo ta zahiri tana fitowa, amma abin dariya da kanta yana da rauni kuma ba shi da mahimmanci musamman saboda alamun fim "mai tsanani" kamar 007 da A Dangerous Mission suna ba da dariya a matsayin babban ɓangaren fim.
Abin dariya yana da kyau ga yara, kuma ba na jin cewa Johnny English yana da hankali da kuma hankali kamar yadda Atkinson ya yi da Mr. Bean.
Wani abu da ake maimaitawa a kowace shekara shi ne cewa Birtaniya tana cikin mawuyacin hali.
Wani dan gwanin kwamfuta ya shiga cikin wani babban asirin hukumar leken asiri ta Burtaniya, ya kuma bayyana sunayen duk wani dan sandan Birtaniya da ke aiki a filin, don ya bata wa wani dan sandan da ke aiki rai, kamar yadda Kevin Eldon ya nuna a matsayin wani dan wasa.
Wannan shi ne na karshe ga wani babban firaminista mai neman mulki wanda ya riga ya shiga cikin rashin amincewa da siyasa: Emma Thompson tana yin duk abin da ta iya a cikin fatar Teresa May, amma rubutun ba ta ba ta isasshen wuri ba.
Idan masu ba da shawara a hukumar leken asiri suka gaya masa cewa an gano dukan 'yan leken asiri da ke filin, sai ya kira wani da ya riga ya bar aikin soja.
Wannan, ba shakka, mai ban sha'awa ne Johnny English a cikin kansa. Yana ciyar da kwanakin ritaya a matsayin malamin makarantar sakandare, amma yana ba da darussan ba tare da izini ba a cikin fasaha mai kyau na leken asiri.
An kai English zuwa taron gaggawa a Whitehall, inda ya sake saduwa da abokin aikinsa mai haƙuri Bough, wanda har yanzu Ben Miller ne.
Bough ya riga ya zama mai iyali, ya auri kwamandan jirgin ruwa wanda Vicki Pepperdine ba ta da damar yin aiki a matsayinta.
Saboda haka, Batman da Robin masu bala'i sun koma cikin asirin majalisa don fuskantar Ophelia Bhuletova, mai aikata laifi mai ban tsoro, wanda Olga Kurylenko ta buga.
A halin yanzu, Firayim Minista na Birtaniya yana fuskantar wata babbar matsala ta hanyar wani mai karfin hali, mai karfin kudi mai karfin kudi, wanda Jason Volta, wanda Jake Lacy ya buga, ya ce zai iya magance matsalar kwamfuta a Birtaniya.
Abinda ya faru shine cewa English da Bough sun zama farce: biyu masu kama da masu jiran abinci sun ƙone gidan cin abinci na Faransa kuma sun haifar da rikici yayin da suke neman su shiga cikin gidan Volta.
Ko da yake masu yin fim ɗin sun kasa yin kome sa'ad da suka isa ƙarshen fim ɗin, duk da haka, duk da cewa fim ɗin yana da ban sha'awa da kuma ban sha'awa, har ila yana da ɗan ƙaramin tasiri ga yara.
Za ka iya ɗaukan fim ɗin a matsayin abin da ya dace.
