Terry Branstad, jakadan Amurka a kasar Sin kuma tsohon gwamnan jihar Iowa ya ce Beijing ta yi wa ma'aikata, manoma da kamfanoni na Amurka lahani, Iowa babbar mai fitar da kayayyakin gona zuwa kasar Sin.
"Kasar Sin yanzu tana kara tayar da kayanta ta hanyar wallafa labaran farfaganda a cikin jaridarmu mai 'yanci", in ji Branstad a cikin wani labarin da aka wallafa a cikin jaridar Des Moines Register a ranar Lahadi.
"Ta hanyar yada farfagandarsu, gwamnatin China tana amfani da al'adun Amurka na 'yancin magana da latsawa ta hanyar sanya tallace-tallace a cikin jaridar Des Moines Register", in ji Branstad.
"A kan titunan jaridu na birnin Beijing, ra'ayoyi masu banbanci suna da iyaka, kuma ra'ayoyin da 'yan kasar Sin ke da su game da ci gaban tattalin arzikin su ba su da iyaka, saboda kafofin watsa labarai suna cikin matasan jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin", in ji shi.
Branstad ya ci gaba da cewa, "ɗaya daga cikin manyan jaridu a China ta kauce wa buga labarin da ta rubuta" amma bai bayyana takarda ba.
Kavanaugh zai kori mata daga jam'iyyar Republican, masu sharhi sun yi gargadin
Masu sharhi sun ce, cewa manyan 'yan jam'iyyar Republican suna goyon bayan da kuma kare dan takarar kujerar kotun koli, Brett Kavanaugh, na iya haifar da adawa, musamman a tsakanin mata masu jefa kuri'a a zaben da ke tafe.
An samu kararraki game da wannan lamarin, kuma yawancin 'yan Republican sun riga sun bayyana cewa suna son ci gaba da jefa kuri'a.
"Ba za a iya kawar da irin waɗannan abubuwa ba", in ji Farfesa Grant Reeher na jami'ar Syracuse Maxwell Institute, a cikin wata kasida da aka buga a jaridar The Hill a ranar Asabar.
Reeher bai yi imanin cewa matakin da Sanata Jeff Flake (Republican, Arizona) ya dauka na minti na karshe game da binciken FBI zai kwantar da hankalin masu jefa kuri'a ba.
"Mata ba za su manta da abin da ya faru jiya ba, kuma ba za su manta ba gobe ko a watan Nuwamba", in ji Karine Jean-Pierre, babban mai ba da shawara da kuma mai magana da yawun kungiyar masu gyara ta MoveOnin, a cikin wata jarida da aka wallafa a babban birnin kasar a ranar Juma'a.
A safiyar ranar Juma'a masu zanga-zanga sun rera waka suna cewa "Laraba tana zuwa" yayin da suke nuna gamsuwarsu a zagayen majalisar dattawa a lokacin da 'yan Republican da ke rike da kwamitin shari'a suka yanke shawarar ci gaba da nadin Kavanaugh, duk da shaidar Dr. Christine Blasey Ford, Mic ta ruwaito.
"Ba za a iya kimanta himma da himmar dimokiradiyya ba", in ji Stu Rothenberg, wani mai sharhi kan siyasa wanda ba shi da wani alaƙa da shafin labarai.
"Mutane suna cewa, 'yan'uwa sun riga sun yi farin ciki sosai, kuma hakan gaskiya ne.
Amma zai iya zama mafi girma musamman a tsakanin mata masu jefa kuri'a da ke kusa da su da kuma matasa masu jefa kuri'a, masu shekaru 18 zuwa 29, waɗanda ba sa yawan jefa kuri'a saboda ba sa son shugaban ƙasa.
Masu sharhi sun yi hasashen cewa za a iya samun tawaye idan 'yan Republican suka amince da amincewar shugaban kasa kafin lokacin da Ford zai gabatar da shaidar cin zarafin wanda ya tsaya takarar shugabancin kasar, inda ya yi zargin cewa ya yi wa 'yan majalisa fyade.
"Wannan ya zama rikici ga jam'iyyar Republican", in ji Michael Steele, tsohon shugaban kwamitin Republican National, ga NBC News a farkon makon da ya gabata.
"Ba wai kawai batun batun kuri'ar kwamitin ba ne ko kuma na karshe ko kuma ko za a yi wa Kavanaugh tambayoyi, amma batun yadda 'yan Republican suka yi da kuma yadda suka bi da Ford", in ji Guy Cecil, shugaban kungiyar 'yan Democrat Priorities USA, a wata hira da ya yi da gidan talabijin.
Amma, jama'ar Amirka suna da ra'ayi biyu game da ko za su yarda da shaidar Ford ko Kavanaugh yayin da ƙarancin rinjaye suka karkata zuwa ga na biyun.
Wani sabon binciken da YouGov ya gudanar ya nuna cewa, kashi 41% na masu amsa sun yi imani da shaidar Ford, ko kuma sun yi imani da shi, yayin da kashi 35 cikin 100 suka ce sun yi imani da Kavanaugh ko kuma sun yi imani da shi.
Bugu da ƙari, kashi 38 cikin ɗari sun ce suna ganin Kavanaugh ya yi ƙarya ko kuma ya yi ƙarya a shaidar da ya bayar, yayin da kashi 30 cikin ɗari suka ce haka ne game da Ford.
Bayan Flake ya ci gaba da wannan lamari, FBI tana binciken zargin da Ford ya yi da kuma na Deborah Ramirez, in ji jaridar The Guardian.
Ford ya shaida wa kwamitin shari'a cewa Kavanaugh ya yi masa barazanar shan giya lokacin da Ford ya kai shekara 17.
Ramirez ya ce wani ɗan takarar babban kotun da ke neman zama a majalisa ya gaya masa cewa yana da jinsi ɗaya a lokacin da suka halarci bikin makaranta a lokacin da suke karatu a jami'ar Yale a shekarun 1980.
Wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo na duniya yana shirin fara sabon intanet a matsayin abin da zai iya yi wa Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo, ya kafa wani kamfani da zai yi gogayya da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Aikinsa na baya-bayan nan, Inrupt, kamfani ne da ke kan hanyar sadarwa ta hanyar Berners-Lee, mai suna Solid.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda aka adana bayanan su da kuma wanda zai iya samun damar yin amfani da kowane irin bayanai.
A cikin hira da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya yi wa Inrupt ba'a cewa manufarsa ita ce "mulkin duniya".
"Ya kamata a yi shi yanzu", in ji shi, yana nuni da kamfanin da yake kafawa.
"Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi.
Aikace-aikacen yana amfani da fasahar Solid don mutane su iya ƙirƙirar Tare da bayanan sirri, ko POD.
Wannan zai iya ƙunsar jerin adiresoshin, takardun rubutu, kalanda, laburaren waƙa, da wasu kayan aiki na sirri da na sana'a.
Yana kama da Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify duk suna kan burauzar yanar gizo a lokaci guda.
Abin da ke na musamman game da ajiyar bayanan sirri shi ne, yana da cikakken iko a kan mai amfani, wanda zai iya samun irin bayanan da yake so.
Kamfanin ya kira shi 'sarrafawa ta mutum ta hanyar bayanai'.
John Bruce, shugaban kamfanin, ya ce manufar Inrupt ita ce samar da albarkatu, aiyuka da kuma basirar da ake bukata don kawo Solid a gaban kowa.
A halin yanzu, kamfanin ya ƙunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, dandalin tsaro da IBM ta saya, wasu masu haɓaka da aka biya don aiki tare da aikin, da kuma ƙungiyar masu shirye-shiryen sa kai.
Masu fasahar kere-kere a duk duniya za su iya gina nasu aikace-aikacen da aka rarraba ta hanyar amfani da kayan aikin da ke cikin shafin intanet na Inrupt, duk wannan yana samuwa a wannan makon.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba su tattauna da Facebook da Google ba game da ko ya kamata a ba mutane cikakken canji inda duk tsarin kasuwancin su ya juya baya dare daya.
"Ba ma tambayar su ko sun yarda da abin da muke yi.
A cikin wata kasida da ya wallafa a Medium ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa Inrupt "ta yi aikin samar da makamashi na kasuwanci da kuma tsarin halittu don daidaito da ingancin sabuwar hanyar sadarwa da aka gina a kan Solid".
A shekara ta 1994, Berners-Lee ya kawo sauyi a duniyar Intanet ta hanyar kafa Ƙungiyar Yanar Gizo ta Duniya a Massachusetts Institute of Technology.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ya kasance mai tasiri a cikin tattaunawar game da tsaka tsaki na yanar gizo.
Berners-Lee zai ci gaba da kasancewa a matsayin wanda ya kafa kuma shugaban World Wide Web Consortium, Web Foundation da Open Data Institute bayan ƙaddamar da Inrupt.
"Ina da matuƙar bege game da sabuwar zamanin yanar gizo", in ji Berners-Lee.
Bernard Vann: Birnin da ke Tunawa da Firist Jarumi na Yaƙin Duniya na Ɗaya
A shekara ta 100 bayan wannan, birnin yana murna domin girmama firist na coci na Ingila da ya lashe lambar yabo ta Victoria Cross.
An ba da lambar yabo ta jaruntaka ga Lt. Col. Reverend Bernard Vann saboda abubuwan da suka faru a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918 a kan harin da aka kai a ƙauyukan Bellenglis da Lehaucourt.
Amma, Vann ya mutu ne bayan an harbe shi da bindiga kwanaki huɗu ba tare da ya taɓa sanin cewa an ba shi babban gata a sojojin Britaniya ba.
'Ya'yansa biyu sun bayyana wani abin tunawa a wani bikin da aka yi a Rushden, Northamptonshire, a ranar Asabar da ta gabata.
Ɗaya daga cikin jikokinsa, Michael Vann, ya ce wannan abin "alamar ne sosai" domin an buɗe abin tunawa daidai shekara 100 bayan nasarar da kakansa ya yi.
A ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918, kamar yadda jaridar London Gazette ta ce, Lt. Col. Vann ya ja-goranci rundunarsa a kan Canal de Saint-Quentin "cikin hazo mai-zafi, da kuma harsashin bindigogi masu-zafi da na'urori masu-shan makamai".
Daga baya ya shiga layin gaba kuma "ya nuna babban jaruntaka" ya jagoranci ci gaban sojojin kafin ya kai hari kan bindigogi. A cikin yakin da ya biyo baya, Vann ya kashe sojojin bindigogi uku da hannunsa.
An kashe Lt. Col. Vann ne a ranar 4 ga Oktoba, 1918  wata daya kafin a kawo karshen yakin.
Michael Vann, mai shekara 72, ya ce aikin da kakansa ya yi "wani abu ne da ba zan taɓa iya cim ma ba, wani abu da ke sa ni daraja".
Michael Vann Ya sauka tare da ɗan'uwansa Dr. James Vann, suna ta yin rawa bayan wani biki da ƙungiyar 'yan wasan kwaikwayo ta Brentwood Imperial Youth Band suka yi.
Michael Vann ya ce 'girma ce a gare shi ya shiga cikin wannan bikin,' ya kuma daɗa cewa 'mutane da yawa suna tunawa da ɗaukakar jarumi na gaskiya.'
