Wani sabon jirgin yakin Jamus ya sake jinkiri
An shirya sabon jirgin ruwan na Jamus ya fara aiki a shekarar 2014, an yi niyyar maye gurbin kayan aikin da suka tsufa a lokacin yakin sanyi, amma ba za a fara aiki da shi ba har zuwa shekara mai zuwa saboda rashin ingantattun tsarin da kuma tsadar kudin da ake kashewa, in ji kafofin watsa labarai na kasar.
A cewar wani jami'in soji da ya yi magana da jaridar Die Zeit, an dage fara aiki da jirgin farko na sabon jirgin Baden-Württemberg zuwa farkon rabin shekarar 2019.
An shirya za ta shiga cikin rundunar a shekarar 2014, amma matsalolin da ke damun 'yan wasan bayan sun ci gaba da damun wannan shiri mai ban sha'awa.
Jirgin ruwa hudu na Baden-Württemberg da aka ba da umarni a cikin 2007 don maye gurbin tsoffin jirgi na Bremen.
Bayanan da ake da su sun nuna cewa za su kasance da makamai masu ƙarfi, da makamai masu linzami don yaƙi da jiragen sama da jiragen ruwa, da kuma fasahar ɓoyewa, kamar su radar reflectivity da infrared da kuma fasahar rage gano siginar sauti.
Abubuwa masu mahimmanci na jirgin sun hada da tsawon rayuwarsa  sabbin jirage za su iya aiki a teku har zuwa shekaru biyu ba tare da ziyartar tashar tashar jiragen ruwa ba.
Duk da haka, jinkiri na ci gaba yana nufin cewa jiragen ruwa masu fasaha  waɗanda ake da'awar cewa suna da niyyar haɓaka tasirin Jamus a ƙasashen waje  sun riga sun tsufa a lokacin da suka shiga sabis, jaridar Die Zeit ta lura.
Frigate F125 da aka yi rashin sa'a ya shiga cikin labarai a shekarar da ta gabata lokacin da rundunar sojin ruwan Jamus ta ƙi amincewa da shi kuma ta mayar da shi ga kamfanin Blohm & Voss a Hamburg.
Wannan shi ne karo na farko da rundunar jiragen ruwa ta mayar da jirgin bayan an kawo shi.
Ba a san dalilin dawowar ba, amma kafofin watsa labarai na Jamus sun yi magana game da "ƙwarewar software da na'ura" da ke sa jirgin ya zama mara amfani don ayyukan yaƙi.
Rashin wadatar software yana da mahimmanci saboda yawan ma'aikatan jirgin na Baden-Württemberg kusan 120, wanda shine rabin ma'aikatan tsoffin jiragen ruwan na Bremen.
Bugu da ƙari, an gano cewa jirgin yana da nauyi mai yawa, wanda ke rage ƙarfinsa kuma yana iyakance damar da rundunar ke da ita don sabuntawa daga baya.
Rhineland-Palatinate, mai nauyin tan 7000, ana ganin ya ninka na irin wannan rukunin jiragen ruwa da Jamus ta yi amfani da su a lokacin Yaƙin Duniya na Biyu sau biyu.
Ban da rashin kayan aiki, akwai matsalar da ke tattare da rage farashin aikin.
An ce farashin ya tashi zuwa babban adadin Euro biliyan 3.1 daga farashin farko na Euro biliyan 2.2.
Matsalar samun sabbin jirage masu saukar ungulu ta bayyana ne bayan an yi gargadin kwanan nan cewa sojojin ruwan Jamus suna raguwa.
Shugaban kwamitin tsaron majalisar dokoki ta Jamus Hans-Peter Bartels ya lura a farkon wannan shekarar cewa jiragen ruwan da za su iya aiki suna "ƙaran"wa.
Hukumar ta ce matsalar ta ƙaru ne bayan shekaru da yawa domin an cire tsofaffin jiragen ruwa daga aiki amma ba a kawo sababbin jiragen ruwa ba.
Ya yi korafin cewa babu wani jirgin ruwan Baden-Württemberg da ya samu damar shiga cikin rundunar.
