Wasu daga cikin munanan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da aka yi a shekarun baya-bayan nan:
2004: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske a arewacin Sumatra a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh na Indonesia ta haifar da tsunami a ranar 26 ga watan Disamba, wanda ya afkawa kasashe 14 inda ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya. Fiye da rabin wadanda suka mutu suna cikin yankin Aceh.
2005: A ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu, an yi girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi a gaɓar yamma na Sumatra.
Daruruwan mutane suka mutu a tsibirin Nias da ke bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 6.8 ta afka kudu da tsibirin Java, tsibirin da ke da mazauna da yawa a ƙasar Indonesia, ta jawo tsunami da ya kai ga gaɓar tekun kudu na tsibirin, ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Wani girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.6 ta afkawa birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin Sumatra ta Yamma.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 suka mutu.
2010: Wani girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 ta afka wa tsibirin Mentawai da ke Sumatra, kuma ta jawo tsunami mai tsawon mita goma, wanda ya halaka ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane kusan 300.
2016: Girgizar kasa ta afkawa yankin Aceh Pidie Jaya, inda ta haifar da bala'i da fargaba yayin da mutane ke tuna da mummunar lalacewar da girgizar kasa da tsunami suka yi a shekarar 2004.
Ba a yi tsunami a wannan lokacin ba, amma mutane fiye da 100 sun mutu sa'ad da gine-ginen suka rushe.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok na Indonesiya, inda ta kashe mutane sama da 500, musamman a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ƙasa ta halaka dubban gine-gine kuma ta bar dubban masu yawon buɗe ido a cikin gidaje na ɗan lokaci.
