A cikin takardun kotu, an ba da hukuncin kisa a kan waɗannan laifuffuka biyu.
Makonni bayan harin, wata kotun tarayya ta gurfanar da Saipov a kan tuhuma guda 22, wanda ya hada da aikata laifuka takwas na kisan kai da taimakon kungiyar ta'addanci. Wannan shi ne laifukan da masu gabatar da kara na tarayya ke amfani da shi a shari'o'in da suka shafi aikata laifuka masu cin zarafi.
Harin ya bukaci "shirye-shirye da shiri sosai", kamar yadda masu gabatar da kara suka bayyana, kuma suka kwatanta yadda Saipov ya aikata abin da suka kira "mugu, mai tsanani da kuma abin kunya".
"Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya yi wa iyalan Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadti, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruch, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco rauni, lahani da kuma asarar rai", in ji sanarwar da ke tattare da tuhumar.
